Swift Transportation Selects Oracle Corporation's Oracle Transportation Management
Tuesday, 17 Apr 2012 08:00am EDT
Swift Transportation Company of AZ, LLC announced that it has selected Oracle Corporation's Oracle Transportation Management as the foundation for its Swift Logistics division. This system will support the company's expanding logistics service offering. Oracle Transportation Management will permit Swift Logistics to offer its customers value added solutions such as integrated and streamlined transportation planning and execution, as well as freight payment for multiple transportation modes on a single platform.Â 
